Privacy Policy
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Hesapmatik handles information when you use the application.
Information We Collect
Hesapmatik does not collect, store, or share any personal information.
The app:
Does not require account creation
Does not request name, email address, phone number, or any personal identifiers
Does not track users
All calculations (VAT, percentage, currency conversion, etc.) are performed locally on the device and are never transmitted to any server.
Data Usage
All data entered into the app is used only to perform calculations
No data is stored, processed, or accessed by the developer
Third-Party Services
Hesapmatik does not use:
Analytics services
Advertising networks
Third-party tracking tools
Data Security
Since no personal or usage data is collected, stored, or transmitted, there is no risk of data exposure.
Childrenâ€™s Privacy
Hesapmatik does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13.
